					<h2>Professional Skills Development Education (PSDE)®</h2>				
		Professional Skills Development Education is a structured learning program designed to equip professionals with industry-relevant expertise, technical competencies, and strategic problem-solving abilities necessary for career advancement and certification. This education framework integrates practical training, leadership development, analytical thinking, and real-world case studies to enhance proficiency in specialized fields such as procurement, supply chain, e-commerce, and tourism management. By aligning with global certification standards, emerging industry trends, regulatory requirements, professional skills development fostercontinuous learning, innovation, and career progression, ensuring that individuals remain competitive and well-prepared to meet evolving business challenges.<strong>Total PSDE required</strong>: 35 PSDE are required every 3 years		
															<img width="631" height="469" src="https://aapscm.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/1-19.png" alt="" srcset="https://aapscm.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/1-19.png 631w, https://aapscm.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/1-19-300x223.png 300w, https://aapscm.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/1-19-600x446.png 600w" sizes="(max-width: 631px) 100vw, 631px" />															
					<h2>Earn and Track Your PDES for Certification Renewal</h2>				
		Fill out the form below to register your Professional Development Units (PDES) for certification renewal. Ensure all information is accurate and attach any necessary documentation for verification.[contact-form-7 id="09de6f7" title="Request PDES for Certificate"]
